@startuml
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam activityBorderColor #A80036
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #A80036
skinparam activityStartColor #A80036
skinparam activityEndColor #A80036
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Flow Dashboard Admin

|#E8F5E9|Frontend|
start
:Admin berhasil login;
:Navigasi ke Dashboard;

|#FFF3E0|API|
:GET /api/admin/dashboard;

|#E3F2FD|Backend|
:Query count paralel (Promise.all);
note right
  - totalUsers (users)
  - totalProviders (provider_profiles)
  - totalCustomers (profiles_customer)
  - totalServices (services)
  - totalOrders (orders)
  - pendingVerifications (provider_profiles WHERE status=pending)
  - totalCategories (categories)
end note
:Kirim data dashboard;

|#FFF8E1|Dashboard|
:Tampilkan stat cards;
note right
  4 kartu statistik utama:
  1. Total Mitra (providers)
  2. Total Pelanggan (customers)
  3. Total Order
  4. Menunggu Verifikasi
end note

|#E3F2FD|Backend|
:GET /api/admin/notifications/counts;
:Hitung semua antrian notifikasi;
note right
  - pendingPayments (order pending_payment)
  - pendingExtensions (extension pending_payment)
  - pendingTaskPayments (custom task pending)
  - pendingTaskPayouts (task completed, payout belum)
  - pendingOrderPayouts (order completed, payout belum)
  - pendingProviders (provider pending verifikasi)
  - openReports (laporan terbuka)
end note

|#FFF8E1|Dashboard|
:Tampilkan badge notifikasi di sidebar;
:Admin dapat navigasi ke menu lain;
stop

note right
  **Endpoint:**
  GET /api/admin/dashboard
  GET /api/admin/notifications/counts
end note

@enduml
